  "detailed_description": "Dive into the enigmatic and terrifying universe of the Backrooms, an infinite labyrinth of rooms and corridors. 𝘽𝘼𝘾𝙆𝙍𝙊𝙊𝙈𝙎: 𝙏𝙝𝙚 𝙇𝙖𝙗𝙮𝙧𝙞𝙣𝙩𝙝 takes you on an immersive first-person horror experience, captured through the grainy, nostalgic aesthetic of VHS tapes from the 80s and 90s. In your quest to escape, be careful, as dangerous entities may be on your path. You can also use your flashlight to navigate the darkest places.",
